Package: dpdquery
Type: Package
Title: Query Health Canada Drug Product Database
Version: 1.0.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Ezinne", "Ndukwe",
      email = "ezinne.ndukwe@mail.utoronto.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre", "cph")
    )
  )
Description: Suite of functions designed to query Health Canada's Drug 
    Product Database(DPD) through component APIs. The DPD is managed by
    Health Canada and provides information on drugs approved and authorized 
    for sale in Canada.
    This package is intended to assist with queries of the DPD for usages in 
    pharmacological, healthcare and public health research and projects. The 
    results are returned in an structured dataframe that can be exported to 
    external files.
    For more information regarding the DPD and the information provided, please 
    consult Health Canada resources and contact their team. 
